  m_Name: D2FR Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - You are Aleksandar yes?
  - 'You: Hmm? Oh umm, yes.'
  - "Good to meet you. I\u2019m a member of a faction of people who believe there
    is a greater identity to the government than what is presented to us. I believe
    you should\u2019ve encountered our leader yesterday."
  - "We are all people of similar age, what we believe as the only people old enough
    to somewhat recall life before and the day of when we were \u201Csaved\u201D
    by this government."
  - "But it doesn\u2019t truly feel like we were \u201Csaved\u201D does it? There
    was more to that day than they may describe, you have that feeling too, don\u2019t
    you?"
  - "You: : I\u2026.. Yes, I think I do. But, they\u2019ve never done any wrong to
    any of us so is there really a need to conspire like this?"
  - "If you know they are not to be trusted then it should be quite believable that
    they may have a greater plan to this \u201Cevacuation\u201D ongoing. "
  - Here, please look this over.
  - "We were taught this dome was built to protect us from \u201Cother governments\u201D
    no? It is clear there is much place that the government wishes to hide from us."
  - Whatever this plan is, it is almost certain it would greatly impact not just
    you, but also your daughter.
  - And we need your help. All of us have lost access to our internet functionality,
    being left only for you and your coworkers, you being the only one suitable to
    work alongside us. Would you be willing?
  - "You: Yes\u2026 I\u2019ll help you so long as it does not put my daughter in
    any danger."
  - Thank you, we will ensure that is the case. We will be in touch later.
  bridgeAfterDialogue: 0
